Here we are learning 
*Deploy a new app version 
*Without stopping the traffic 
*Without breaking scaling
*wihtout touching runnnig instance 

This is called as immutable + rolling deployment 

Create a new AMI -> updates  launch template version -> ASG replace instances globally 

Services Involved : 

Services                                 Role 

AMI                            Application version 
LaunchTemplate                 points to AMI
Target Group                   Health-checks  new instances 
ALB                            Keeps traffic flowing 


